OL,6,FSome of the paramedics' colleagues had
OL,7,Fgathered at Jersey's Royal Court
OL,8,Fthroughout the trial to show their
OL,9,Fsupport.
OL,11,FThe prosecution described it as a
OL,12,F"sad, troubling case" and presiding
OL,13,FCommissioner Sir John Saunders said,
OL,14,F"There was no malice from the
OL,15,Fdefendants".
OL,17,FHe added that "the jurats took this
OL,18,Fdecision with anxious and serious
OL,19,Fconsideration".
