OL,3,CMedics guilty of failing to care for
OL,4,Cman who died from cardiac arrest
OL,6,FFollowing the verdict, Chief Ambulance
OL,7,FOfficer, Peter Gavey said: "I would
OL,8,Flike to publicly apologise to Mr
OL,9,FIrvine's family for what happened
OL,10,Fwhile he was in our care. I can only
OL,11,Fimagine how painful this has been for
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,F"We have never forgotten that a man
OL,15,Fdied during this incident and Frazer
OL,16,FIrvine and his family have always been
OL,17,Fat the forefront of our minds during
OL,18,Fthis case.
