OL,3,CMedics guilty of failing to care for
OL,4,Cman who died from cardiac arrest
OL,6,F"Cases of this kind are extremely rare
OL,7,Fand the public can be reassured that
OL,8,Fthe States of Jersey Ambulance Service
OL,9,Fis committed to upholding the highest
OL,10,Fstandards of care and patient safety."
OL,12,FSutherland and Le Sauteur have been
OL,13,Fsuspended from service since 23 March
OL,14,F2022 and will continue to be suspended
OL,15,Fwhile internal investigations start
OL,16,Ffollowing the conclusion of the trial.
OL,18,FA date will be set for sentencing in
OL,19,Fdue course.
